---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';

// Custom styling for the About page
---

<style>
  .about-hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .about-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.7) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 100%);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .about-hero img {
    clip-path: polygon(
      0 0, 
      100% 0, 
      100% calc(100% - 30px), 
      calc(100% - 30px) 100%, 
      0 100%
    );
    filter: contrast(1.1) saturate(1.2);
  }
  
  .about-hero-content {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 2rem;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 80%;
  }
  
  .about-hero-title {
    font-family: 'Bangers', cursive;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 #000, -3px -3px 0 #000, 3px -3px 0 #000, -3px 3px 0 #000;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .about-hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .about-hero-content {
      bottom: 1rem;
      left: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<Layout
	title="About MangaVerse"
	description="Discover the story behind MangaVerse (Manhva-oppa), your AI-powered manga and manhwa recommendation platform"
	pubDate={new Date('May 09 2025')}
>
	<div class="about-hero" slot="hero">
		<img src="/images/about-hero.jpg" alt="Manga Collection Bookshelf" />
		<div class="about-hero-content">
			<h1 class="about-hero-title">About MangaVerse</h1>
			<p class="about-hero-subtitle">Your AI-powered manga and manhwa discovery platform</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="manga-panel p-6 bg-black/40 mb-8">
		<h2 class="manga-title text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4">Our Story</h2>
		<p class="mb-4">
			Welcome to <strong>MangaVerse</strong> (also known as Manhva-oppa), your ultimate destination for discovering manga and manhwa tailored to your unique tastes. Founded in 2024, our platform was born from a simple passion: connecting readers with stories they'll love.
		</p>
		<p>
			As avid manga and manhwa enthusiasts ourselves, we understood the challenge of finding new series in an ever-expanding sea of content. That's why we created MangaVerse—to harness the power of AI and community to make discovering your next favorite read effortless and exciting.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
		<div class="manga-border p-6 bg-black/30">
			<h2 class="manga-title text-xl mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">
				At MangaVerse, we believe that the perfect manga or manhwa exists for everyone—it's just a matter of finding it. Our mission is to create the most intuitive, personalized recommendation system that understands not just what you've enjoyed in the past, but why you enjoyed it.
			</p>
			<p>
				We're committed to supporting both readers and creators by fostering a vibrant community where great stories can be discovered, discussed, and celebrated.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="manga-border p-6 bg-black/30">
			<h2 class="manga-title text-xl mb-4">AI-Powered Discovery</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">
				What makes MangaVerse special is our advanced AI recommendation engine. Unlike traditional systems that only look at genres or popularity, our technology analyzes hundreds of factors—from art styles and narrative techniques to character development and thematic elements.
			</p>
			<p>
				The more you use MangaVerse, the smarter it becomes, learning your preferences and surprising you with discoveries that perfectly match your unique taste profile.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2 class="manga-title text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-6">Key Features</h2>

	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
		<div class="manga-panel p-4 bg-black/30 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
			<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"></path></svg>
			</div>
			<h3 class="manga-title text-lg mb-2">Personalized Recommendations</h3>
			<p class="text-sm">Our AI analyzes your reading history and preferences to suggest manga and manhwa you'll love.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="manga-panel p-4 bg-black/30 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
			<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
			</div>
			<h3 class="manga-title text-lg mb-2">Community Engagement</h3>
			<p class="text-sm">Connect with fellow fans, share recommendations, and participate in discussions about your favorite series.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="manga-panel p-4 bg-black/30 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
			<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"></path><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"></path></svg>
			</div>
			<h3 class="manga-title text-lg mb-2">Comprehensive Library</h3>
			<p class="text-sm">Access our extensive database of manga and manhwa, complete with detailed information, ratings, and reviews.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="manga-panel p-6 bg-black/40 mb-8">
		<h2 class="manga-title text-2xl mb-4">The Team Behind MangaVerse</h2>
		<p class="mb-4">
			Our team consists of passionate manga and manhwa enthusiasts, talented developers, and AI specialists who share a common goal: creating the ultimate platform for discovering and enjoying Asian comics.
		</p>
		<p>
			We're constantly working to improve MangaVerse, adding new features, expanding our library, and refining our recommendation algorithms to provide you with the best possible experience.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="manga-border p-6 bg-black/30 mb-8">
		<h2 class="manga-title text-xl mb-4">Join Our Community</h2>
		<p class="mb-4">
			MangaVerse is more than just a recommendation platform—it's a growing community of manga and manhwa lovers from around the world. We invite you to create an account, customize your profile, and start discovering amazing stories today.
		</p>
		<p>
			Have suggestions or feedback? We'd love to hear from you! Our platform is constantly evolving based on user input, so don't hesitate to reach out and help us make MangaVerse even better.
		</p>
		<div class="mt-6">
			<a href="/register" class="manga-border inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-red-500/20 hover:bg-red-500/30 transition-colors">
				Join MangaVerse Today
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
